## Take action

The Zoning By-Law renewal comes up for a public hearing on October 16. Please use [Grow Together Edmonton's tool](https://www.gtyeg.ca/#take-action) to email your councillor in support of the renewal. If you can, please sign up to speak atht epublic hearing. Signing up only takes a minute:

1.  [Follow this link](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfjK1JQOPRWVORUVKsSbRn3yLN5E9vcVLu3nifMO4N1ZfmgFg/viewform)

2.  Select "Public Hearing" and enter October 16 as the date

3.  Where it asks for the agenda number and title, enter: 3.1 Zoning Bylaw Renewal

4.  Select "In Favour" as your position
